title: P
description: I want to help clean up the lot before it becomes a park. Could we get a clean-up group organized for this? I’m available on the weekends and after school on weekdays.

title: Latin Music Fest
description: I think it would be great to have an annual Latin music festival each summer in mi parque. We could have a mix of local musicians and Chicago-wide musicians.

title: Peace Parade
description: What if we had a parade between two of the parks, kind of like a peace parade with a community picnic at the end.

title: Time for Girls
description: My friends and I want to play basketball but there is always a group of guys on the court. Could we have a “Girl-time only” for the field & basketball courts?
